    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p>State Wide Real Estate Listing Service has been created to assist the real estate brokers and agents in the area in which they serve. It is not intended to replace the local listing agencies, but rather to act as an aid to enhance brokers and agents across the state. The name, State Wide Real Estate Listing Service, has been abbreviated to SWRELS.com. Several, but not all of the advantages of State Wide real Estate Listing Service include:</li>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <strong>Affordable</strong><br />One of our mottos is "Making real estate listings affordable for every agent". Our goal is to always keep listing properties to the very lowest cost possible.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Market Expansion</strong><br />By having a web site for your state, that covers the entire state, we are making it easier for the agent as well as the consumer to keep in touch with the area in which he or she may serve or have an interest.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Unlimited Listings</strong><br />This web site offers its members the advantage of unlimited listings. You will never run out of space to list and advertise your properties.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>User Friendly</strong><br />The site has an easy to use system for agents to navigate without having to search for properties from multiple sites. The keywords search feature will allow agents to list only their properties for review without logging in, click here for a list of keywords.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Precise</strong><br />The site will get you to the specifics. You can choose exactly what you want to list as an agent.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Information</strong><br />SWRELS.com will endeavor to keep agents informed about matters of importance. Agent participation is encouraged through the feedback link on the agent page. Every idea or suggestion will be read and analyzed. If it is feasible, then SWERLS.com will endeavor to incorporate that idea into the system.
            </li>
            <li>
                <strong>Visible</strong><br />SWRELS.com will strive to keep this site in the forefront of major search engines. Media advertising will also play an important role as well.
            </li>
        </ul>
